Name: Average time for Completed + Resolved when it directly follows Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Minimum time for Completed + Resolved after Accepted + In Progress in cases where Completed + In Call occurs earlier in the trace
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average time from Completed + In Call to Completed + Resolved
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Time of Completed + Resolved in traces containing the subsequence Completed + In Call → Accepted + In Progress → Completed + Resolved
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Elapsed time between Completed + In Call and Completed + Resolved across all variants where both activities occur
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average time for Completed + Resolved when preceded by Accepted + Wait - User compared to when preceded by Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Minimum time for Completed + Resolved in the variant: Accepted + In Progress → Accepted + In Progress → Completed + In Call
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Cycle Time of Completed + Resolved in cases that transition from Completed + In Call back to Accepted + In Progress before reaching Completed + Resolved
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Total time for Completed + Resolved in variants starting with Queued + Awaiting Assignment versus those starting with Accepted + In Progress and containing Completed + In Call
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Time from Accepted + In Progress to Completed + Resolved when Completed + In Call is executed in between
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average time for Completed + Resolved in high-frequency variants (frequency > 100) that include Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + Resolved' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Minimum time for Completed + Resolved following Completed + In Call without any intermediate waiting states (e.g., no Accepted + Wait - User, Accepted + Wait - Vendor, etc.)
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Total time for Completed + Resolved in the variant: Accepted + In Progress → Accepted + In Progress → Completed + In Call → Accepted + In Progress → Completed + Resolved → Completed + Closed
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Total resolution time of Completed + Resolved grouped by whether Completed + In Call appears in the same case
